	‚Ä¢	electrical storage
	‚Ä¢	computation
	‚Ä¢	simulation

inside cells would:
	‚Ä¢	disrupt ion gradients
	‚Ä¢	generate heat
	‚Ä¢	interfere with signaling

Mitochondria work because ATP chemistry is already native. Silicon-style computation is not.

3. Evolution vs engineering

Mitochondrial integration:
	‚Ä¢	had no design
	‚Ä¢	tolerated massive failure
	‚Ä¢	killed countless lineages

Human augmentation:
	‚Ä¢	cannot ethically use that process
	‚Ä¢	cannot accept that failure rate
	‚Ä¢	cannot wait geological timescales

That alone rules out true biological endosymbiosis.

